  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">A science teacher is preparing the 5&nbsp;stations of a science laboratory. Each station will have either Experiment&nbsp;A materials or Experiment&nbsp;B materials, but not both. Experiment&nbsp;A requires 6&nbsp;teaspoons of salt, and Experiment&nbsp;B requires 4&nbsp;teaspoons of salt. If <span class=\"italic\">x</span> is the number of stations that will be set up for Experiment&nbsp;A and the remaining stations will be set up for Experiment&nbsp;B, which of the following expressions represents the total number of teaspoons of salt required?</p>\n",
